---
title: Chicken and Chickpea Curry with Buttery Rice
description: Speedy curries are a weeknight hero! Chickpeas add extra heartiness to this filling feast, while ginger and fragrant curry paste add all the flavour of a slow-cooked sauce in a fraction of the time!
